VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT Query\(\s*fmt\.Sprintf|Exec\(\s*fmt\.Sprintf|Raw\(\s*fmt\.Sprintf
WHEN EXPR MISSING:prepare|parameterize|\?.*args|sqlx\.NamedExec|squirrel
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects dynamic SQL construction via string formatting.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Echo SQL Query Concatenation Sink.
